#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When you send messages or requests with clients that don't propagate the OpenTelemetry context you will have incomplete traces or broken traces, when the destination creates spans but because no context was propagated, the parent span is non-existent. This will cause more than one trace per request, which will cause problems."
msgstr "当您使用无法传播 OpenTelemetry 上下文的客户端发送消息或请求时，将会出现不完整的追踪或断裂的追踪。这是因为目标端虽然创建了跨度，但由于未传播上下文，导致父跨度不存在。这将导致每个请求产生多个追踪，从而引发问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
