#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*This is an advanced subject*. For more details on context propagation please check the above section about <<propagators-reference>>."
msgstr "*这是一个高级主题* 。有关上下文传播的更多详细信息，请参阅上文关于 <<propagators-reference>> 的部分。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
