msgstr "`createParentContext()` 方法介绍了如何创建一个 OpenTelemetry 上下文。在此情况下，我们会生成默认的 link:https://www.w3.org/TR/trace-context/[W3C 跟踪上下文] 标头： `traceparent` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "the `receiveAndUseContext()` method receives the contents of the `traceparent` header used to bootstrap a new OpenTelemetry context in the destination."
msgstr "`receiveAndUseContext()` 方法接收 `traceparent` 标头的内容，该内容用于在目标位置初始化一个新的 OpenTelemetry 上下文。"

